#Text=DS : It ’s not all Gene Loves Jezebel sounding .
#Text=PG : No.
#Text=Satanic music is specific to each person .
#Text=So to me , Satanic music is the symphony , which to me is the highest art form .

#Text=So Beethoven , Mahler , Bruckner , Shostakovich — to me that ’s some of the most Satanic music ever written because the architecture is there , the expressivity is there ; the reflection on the human condition is all present and it ’s not idealistic .
#Text=It ’s mostly questioning or showing what a human is capable of doing .
#Text=And I love architecture .
#Text=Cathedrals are wonderful .
#Text=I have no hatred of those because they are put to religious use .
#Text=They have symbols on them , but I know those are just symbols .
#Text=I love skyscrapers too .
#Text=Anton LaVey 's children and estate
#Text=DS : Do Dr. LaVey ’s children have anything to do with the church at all ?
#Text=PG : His son Xerxes is a member because he asked to be .
#Text=We generally do n't let people under 18 join .
#Text=We used to let people whose parents allowed them to join , but because people are so litigious we changed that .
#Text=We just do n't want to take the chance that some parents say , “ Yes , it ’s okay if my kid joins the Church of Satan , ” and then decides that ’s the reason they ca n't control their kid .
#Text=We ’re just not willing to go there .
#Text=But if our members have children who are interested , they can participate and become members , but that ’s the only way you can if you ’re not legally an adult .
#Text=So Xerxes could become a member because his mother was High Priestess at one point , and still remains a member .
#Text=DS : But not Zeena ?
#Text=PG : No , she left years ago .
#Text=She ’s not very bright and is very jealous .
#Text=She and her paramour , Nikolas Shreck , got married I think .
#Text=They wanted to take the Church of Satan over at one point and wanted Anton LaVey to retire , but he was a feisty guy and said " Hell no !
